pings
=====

Captures highlighted messages in HexChat and lets you review them.

Usage
-----

pings records highlighted messages for you to recall.

    /pings [date] [time]

shows all highlighted messages since that date and time. Date must be MM-DD,
and time must be hh:mm[:ss].

